result:
div.padding-large
  div.flex.wide.justify-space-between
    //- :Left
    div: h2 Orders

    //- Right
    switcher(inline-template)
      div
        a.padding(@click="active='all'" :class="{'active':active=='all'}") All
        a.padding(@click="active='paid'" :class="{'active':active=='unprocessed'}") Unprocessed
        a.padding(@click="active='due'" :class="{'active':active=='for pickup'}") For Pickup
  
  //- Contents
  table.wide
    tr
      td
        h3 Stephen John Raymundo
        h5 For Pickup
      td
        button.float-right Edit
    tr
      td
        h3 Newborn Packages
        span Short Description
      td
        button.float-right(@click='$refs.order.show()') View

  modal(ref="order" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding Order Details
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            table.wide
              thead
                tr
                  th Print Size
                  th Filename
                  th Price
              tr
                td 8x10
                td DSC_0012
                td Php 100
              tr
                td 8x10
                td DSC_0012
                td Php 100
              tr  
                td 8x10
                td DSC_0012
                td Php 100
              
                
            div.flex.wide
              button.flex-grow Cancel Request
              button.flex-grow.margin-left-small For Pickup
